Anyone up for 9 holes this Sunday? Tewksbury Country Club is a nice 9 hole course. Looking for a few more players to join. I can book a tee time for us on Friday (2 days in advance), and will probably play around 11am. If you'd like to join, let me know time preference.

$24 for 9 holes. $9 per person for golf cart. Please bring $1 for website maintenance if you are playing.

www.tewksburycc.com

Let me know if any questions.

Thanks!
Chuck Robbins
